    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p><addressee>Rev: Mr Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">D. Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">In the Episcopal Recorder<lb/> of this city, is an article upon the
                subject<lb/> of “<hi rend="underline">The Jews</hi>” that interested me very
                much,<lb/> and I would like much to see it republished<lb/> in the Occident with
                such comments as<lb/> may choose to make—or the comments<lb/> without the piece. I
                would like to see both<lb/> in your <del>paper</del> periodical, <hi
                    rend="underline">first</hi>
                <sic>becuse</sic> some<lb/> of us have seen it and have hardly known<lb/> what to
                say or think respecting it: the views<lb/> presented was somewhat new to us,—and<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">secondly</hi>, it is written with so much candor<lb/> and
                fairness that I think its republication<lb/> as suggested will have a good
                    <sic>effects</sic> upon<lb/> the feelings of Jews and Gentiles towards<lb/> each
                other. You will find it in the Episcopal<lb/> Recorder printed by
                        <persName>Stoody<add>?</add></persName> or the <date>2 of August</date>
                Inst.</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Respectfully yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">Samuel</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>Received at the <placeName>Phil</placeName> PO<lb/> under cover from
                    <placeName>Wilkes Barre Pa</placeName><lb/>
                <date>Aug 8/37</date></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Rev: Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
